author: lgo
msg: ra_serf: Fixed regression introduced in 1.5 - r27538 that breaks the replay
(start_replay): revstart_func is only set when using the replay_range API.
(end_replay): revfinish_func is only set when using the replay_range API.
(svn_ra_serf__replay): Define a series of missing fields on the parser ctx and
replay ctx. Those fields were introduced to support the callbacks introduced
with replay_range. Also, when the REPORT request is created, send it to the
server, the chance that a reply will be returned is much greater that way.
